Elements to Build Computer Memory Simulations From

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cache
    Models the Physical Cache
    CacheController
    Models L1-Ln Cache Memory
    CacheStatistics
    Tracks Cache Statistics
    Memory
    Models the Main System Memory of a Computer
    MemoryBlock
    Models a Block of Memory That Is Transfered Between (and Stored In) Levels of Cache and Memory
    MemoryElement
    Models the Elements of a MemoryBlock
    MemoryResult
    Wrapper for a Result From a Memory Request

Package edu.arizona.ece.memsim.model Description

Elements to Build Computer Memory Simulations From

Inheritance from these modules is encouraged and should be placed in edu.arizona.ece.memsim.implementations.(Name of Implementation).model
